{"tid":2316192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國因應香港問題制裁14名全國人大常委會副委員長","createTime":"2020-12-07T16:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T04:43:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3864e303d1ad3c51a8ad8f6b5ff8a3bef6a7bdb6","tid":2316192,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564077-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564077-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7Cukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=1935a733\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564077-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7424803e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564077-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國財政部因應香港問題，制裁14名全國人大代表。<br />\n<br />\n被制裁的14人，全部都是全國人大常委會副委員長，包括王晨、曹建明、張春賢、沈躍躍、吉炳軒、艾力更依明巴海、萬鄂湘、陳竺、王東明、白瑪赤林、丁仲禮、郝明金、蔡達峰及武維華。<br />\n<br />\n路透社早前報道，華府實施制裁的原因，是這批人涉及取消香港多名民主派人士的議員資格。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部昨日表示，中方已經多次表明，一直堅決反對，並強烈譴責美方藉香港問題干涉中國內政，對中方人員實施所謂的制裁，敦促美方立即停止插手香港事務，停止干涉中國內政，若果美方一意孤行，中方必將繼續採取堅決反制措施，捍衛國家的主權安全利益。"},{"pid":"939faaf318cc4c5cdd9173b0ef9cda8742d1c84d","tid":2316192,"uid":11793,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"口交部宣布出兵打美國未啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc23f56b74ec4d01421e5f2fea722715352201d","tid":2316192,"uid":32473,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:39:56.000Z","msg":"幾正<br />\n搵返個temple 就出得聲明"},{"pid":"5909e55f656916dcfaf40d436bcdb7471775e3f8","tid":2316192,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMnUdBZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMnUdBZ.